Package: securedrop-monitor
Source: securedrop-monitor
Version: 0.2.1
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: SecureDrop Team <securedrop@pressfreedomfoundation.org>
Depends: securedrop-monitor-hardening,securedrop-monitor-ossec
Section: web
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://pressfreedomfoundation/securedrop
Description: SecureDrop Monitor Server (metapackage depending on the latest version)
 This is a metapackage to install the securedrop-monitor-hardening and
 the securedrop-interfaces-ossec packages. You will need to run
 /opt/securedrop/post-install.sh to see auth values for ssh and the document
 interface. Without this information you will be locked out of the servers.
